<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm229641152"><term>corporate culture</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm258275120">The beliefs and behaviors that determine how a company’s employees and management interact inside an organization and also handle outside business transactions. Corporate culture develops organically over time from the cumulative traits of the leaders and the people that the company hires.</meaning>
</definition>
